Interface RICededPremiumAdapter

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    RICededPremium
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface RICededPremiumAdapter

      • createAndAddHistory

        RICededPremiumHistory createAndAddHistory(java.util.Date recalcDate,
                                          RIRecalcReason reason,
                                          java.lang.String comment)
        Create a new RICededPremiumHistory entity associated with this RICededPremium entity.
        Parameters:
        recalcDate - The creation time for any new ceding transactions created with this history.
        reason - The reason (typekey) for the creation of cedings
        comment - A text comment that may be associated with this history
        Returns:
        a new entity which implements RICededPremiumHistory and refers to this RICededPremium.
